Final recipe :
lady fingers (not boudoirs)

3 egg yellow
3 egg white
250g mascarpone
45g sugar
10cl creme liquide

2 gelatine sheets : il faut la fondre
	https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QRHUthKLNjw
3 esspressos
	+ 20g amaretto
		NOT CHEAP ONE
Use smaller moule

--
gelatine : 
	dans eau froide
---
1 gelatine sheets
3 egg yellow
3 egg white
250g mascarpone
50g sugar
150g creme fleurette

gelatine is to be melted then added to mascarpone
---
Back to real tiramisu :

1 gelatine sheets
3 egg yellow
3 egg white
40g sugar
Lombardy Amaretto 


----------------
gelatine in glas of cold water
egg yellow + sugar mix up well
	heat in bain marie
	mix
	add gelatine
	mix

egg white + salt
	monte but not too much
		otherwise wont mix up

add in egg white

cold creme fraiche liquide
	monte but not too much

mix in
